c: 59
v: 23
t: "“Iye ndi Allah, Amene palibenso wina wopembedzedwa mwachoonadi koma Iye, Mfumu, Woyera, Mwini mtendere, Wotsimikizira (aneneri Ake mphamvu yochitira zozizwitsa,) Msungi wa chilichonse (yemwe akuona zochita za akapolo Ake;) Wamphamvu zopambana, Mgonjetsi Wotukuka muulemelero; Wamkulukulu. Wayeretsedwa Allah kuzimene akumuphatikiza nazo"